{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Increase minimum sentences for drug supply offences",
        "additional_details": "Too many people have lost their lives and we believe this is escalating. Greater deterrents need to be put in place to protect life.",
        "background": "Drug supply should not be considered a victimless crime. Aggravating factors such as supply to vulnerable people and minors should be given greater consideration. ",
